The evidence with the title 'Donald Trump wants to deport 11 million migrants: is that even ... ' says Aug 27, 2015  ... Trump has not said how he would handle cases in which the legal US residents in question preferred to stay put . In such cases, presumably, the families would be broken up after all , because while Trump is famous for saying “ you're fired!” , no president has the power to tell a US citizen : “ you're deported!” . 
